{"tid":1822974,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府稱會適時將《國歌法條例草案》交立會大會恢復二讀辯論","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T11:43:23.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0b294e4071d0ffb09313c1a80d3632fe16a4f58e","tid":1822974,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員、基本法委員會委員梁美芬批評，民主派議員企圖癱瘓立法會內務委員會，主要目的是要拖跨國歌法本地立法。她說，如果未能進行本地立法程序，唯有直接公布在本港實施。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨陳淑莊質疑梁美芬的講法，認為中央與特區政府已選擇以本地立法，而非採用「當地公布」的形式。<br />\n<br />\n政府回應《條例草案》草擬經過嚴謹程序，當局會適時把草案提交立法會大會以恢復二讀辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502160-20200110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502160-20200110.htm&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d0a98407\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502160-20200110.htm&h=f724939d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502160-20200110.htm</a>"},{"pid":"618543b78790a705ca4db674f97fc6f73e733337","tid":1822974,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"ok，趁運動個火就嚟熄又點返熱佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ec5d5698fa8ba700dc26805231dc374cf86059","tid":1822974,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"【中大有人同警開閉門會議！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2754b25eede924d199bb77a260b6e45bd3d81728","tid":1822974,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88b043cc1cdecd9fd654497ff4acf4d1954602e","tid":